title: Richard Dawkins - Enemies Of Reason (Pt2 The Irrational Health S
description:
Part Two of Richard Dawkins&#039; BBC Channel Four program entitled "Enemies Of Reason - The Irrational Health System".  Dawkins presents strong and valid arguments against the modern return to so-called alternative or ancient medicines.

There&#039;s a little audio de-sync in the early parts of the file, but it comes out fine in the latter two-thirds.  Hope its not too distracting, but this was after seven attempts to tweak this into complete synch and this was the best I could do.  Please enjoy and SEED!
